column4: Hey guys, I can't get Azureus OR BitTornado working.  What the heck is going on?  Has anyone had trouble torrenting?  Does anyone know of a good app?
What if I don't want to bloody use Wine for a bloody torrent program?!
then your life just sucks, do us all a favor and end it.
Sorry for yelling at you.  I am frustrated.
I apologize, I was out of line.
Apology accepted, dude.  I shouldn't have shouted.  You were just trying to help.
Do you happen to be familiar with OiNK.me.com?
Never heard of it.  What's its story?
Nothing in particular. Torrent tracker, and I can't get it to work.
Are you behind a router?  That always screws up BT
I think OiNK just doesn't like me.
